<br>
pets can't be used to MT while someone is in range for the mob to hit if its on their hate list.  Mobs will always go after PCs on the hate list first, then hit the mob if nothing else is in range. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=merlota>Merlota</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 47<br> <font color=#333333>(1/29/03 5:23:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=974.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: pet aggro</span><hr size=1> /em glares at the enchanters<br>
