&quot;but DS's don't add agro, which in this case you want.&quot;<br>
---------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
Damage shields DO!! cause aggro.  <br>
<br>
<br>
The damage the shields do is attributed to environment for XP purposes, but for Aggro purposes it is attributed to the mob they hit.  <br>
